               <p>Mr. Risley depos'd, That on the 14th of Feb. at 11 at Night, between <placeName id="t17280501-34-crimeloc180">Hammersmith and Chiswick</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17280501-34-crimeloc180" type="placeName" value="Hammersmith and Chiswick"></interp>
